    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that those old views were biased, but if we look at it from a strictly evolutionary or sociological standpoint today, is there any objective way to say one structure is more \"advanced\" than another? like, is there a real difference in human capability or cognitive complexity between these groups, or is it just a matter of different ways of living?",
